[Black "The brave and the KID II #1"]
[Result "*"]

1. b3
{ We just give Black the centre, and a false sense of security... only to take all of it back with interest at the right time! }
1... Nf6 2. Bb2 g6 { 'Two can play this game!' } 3. Nf3 Bg7 4. g3
{ We just take it one step further and aim for a double fianchetto! } 4... O-O
5. Bg2
{ This is a major tabiya, there are many ways for Black to continue here. }
5... c5 6. c4
{ Stopping Black from achieving both c5 and d5. It is the essential point in our strategy. I faced the following line a lot during my blitz/bullet run. }
6... d5 7. cxd5 Qxd5 8. Nc3 Qh5 9. h3
{ An important move which kills off any hope for Black. One noob refused to accept his error and went for }
9... Nc6 10. g4 { Ends up losing a piece 😀. } *

[Event "?"]
