{ with the idea to bring the knight to e5 via c4. } 10... Be7 11. Nc4 O-O 12.
d4
{ With a slightly more comfortable Catalan type of edge due to more active pieces and future invasion on c6 😀. }
12... cxd4 13. Nxd4 Nxd4 14. Qxd4 { Endgame is welcome for us! } 14... Qxd4 15.
Bxd4
