{ This would be a very respectable and natural choice in blitz. } 7. Nf3
{ I like this direction more, as we can get an advantage if Black plays natural moves. }
7... Bd6 8. d3 { Stopping any e4 ideas. If Black goes for... } 8... Qe7
{ After  8...O-O  9.Nbd2  we are doing great, as we can continue with our plans of Be2-O-O-b4-Nc4 etc. }
9. Nbd2
{ We delay Be2 as the bishop has more amazing prospects in a different dimension! }
9... O-O 10. g3
{ Since Black was ready for f5 and kingside attack... with this move, we are getting ready for it! }
10... Bg4 11. Qc1
{ Sidestepping any aggressive ideas and preparing to finish the kingside development peacefully. I decided not to allow  11.Qc2  Bc5  , as now there are threats on e3. }
*

