9... Qe7 10. Qc2 { Protecting our bishop and getting ready for Nf3. } 10... f5
11. Ngf3 e4 { Black is trying to cash in before we finish our development... }
12. dxe4 Bxb2 13. Qxb2
{ We are happy to have exchanged the dark-squared bishop, making the weak king a permanent liability. }
13... fxe4 14. Nd4 { The e4-pawn could become a long term weakness/target. }
14... Ne5 15. Nxe4 Ng4 16. Qc2
{ The comp is showing some compensation for Black. Please ask him what he is talking about. 😀 }
