7... O-O 8. Nf3
{ In the Be7 line, we delay d3 for one more move to have the Bd3 idea ready. }
8... Bf6 { This is the most popular move. } 9. d3 { Say No to e4 ideas! } 9...
Re8 10. Nbd2 { Ne4 incoming! } 10... g6 11. Be2 Bg7 12. O-O
{ Black just lost two tempi to reach this position: he could have just played 6...g6 and be done with it. 😀   In any case, our plan is to play b4, Rfc1-Ne4 etc. }
*

