3... exd4 4. Qxd4 Nc6 5. Qd2
{ The best place for the queen, not getting in the way of our queenside castling. }
5... d5 6. e3
{ Followed by Ne2 - Nc3 - O-O-O - Nf4 plans with full flow of attack and initiative for us thanks to the play against the d5-pawn. }
