d4 { Strike them when it's hot! } 5... e4 6. e3 Bg7 7. Nge2
{ As a rule after Black commits e4, our g1-knight should head to f4. } 7... O-O
8. Nf4 { The knight is well placed on f4. } 8... c6 9. Be2
{ With an interesting French type position. } 9... Na6 10. O-O d5 11. cxd5 cxd5
12. Ba3
{ The bishop had to find a new destiny, since his current one wasn't looking so great anymore! }
12... Re8 13. Nb5 Bf8 14. Bxf8 Rxf8 15. Rc1
{ We have some play on the queenside and also there are ideas involving f3. } *

