{ Forcing the exchange of the dark-squared bishop which will permanently weaken Black's king. }
12... Bxb2 13. Qxb2 { When the bishop falls... the queen rises! } 13... Qf6 14.
Qxf6 { ENDGAME! } 14... Nxf6 15. Bg2
{ With a stable endgame pull thanks to the superior material imbalance of Rook + Bishop vs Rook + Knight. }
