Nxd5 13. Nfxd5 cxd5 14. Rxd5 { No guts no glory! - Vidit Gujarathi, 2021. }
14... Qe8 15. Qd2 { With an evil laugh. 😀 } 15... Bc6 16. Bg2
{ This was our beautiful point giving up the exchange to save our dignity and honour! }
