7... Nh5 { Black could try to be very funny, trying to prepare f5 or e5. } 8.
c4 { We just continue taking control of the center and space. } 8... e5 9. Nc3
{ Followed by e4 with a big advantage and easy play for us. The knight is still looking for a noble cause on h5. 😀 }
