1. b3
{ We just give Black the centre with a false sense of security, only to take it all back with interest at the right time! }
1... c5 2. Bb2 Nc6 3. c4 { If Black tries to copy us with the fianchetto } 3...
b6 4. g3 { Yup this is the one! } 4... Bb7 5. Bg2 Nf6 6. Nf3 e6
{ Black really can't develop the bishop in any other way. } 7. O-O Be7 8. d4
{ Space... } 8... cxd4 9. Nxd4 O-O 10. Nc3
