{ Stupid Comp! what is the bishop doing on a6?? How do you expect me to explain this to our dear viewers :@@EndBracket@@? The bishop is attacking the c4-pawn which is supported by a pawn?? Is that what you want?? Happy now? }
7. Nc3 Rc8
{ Black is waiting...biding his time as it was too early to develop the kingside bishop due to ideas like d4. }
8. a3
{ Waiting for Black to commit Be7...@@StartBracket@@Continuing to bully Black@@EndBracket@@ }
8... Be7 9. g4 { Here we go! } 9... O-O 10. g5 Ne8 11. h4
{ with good attacking chances on the kingside. } *

