1. b3
{ We just give Black the centre with a false sense of security, only to take it all back with interest at the right time! }
1... c5 2. Bb2 Nc6 3. c4
{ The move order is very important, we delay Nf3 for the time being. } 3... Nf6
4. e3 { One of the toughest lines I had to fight against was the solid } 4...
e6 5. Nf3
{ After  5...d5  6.cxd5  either recapture will lead to the QGD chapter. } 5...
Be7
{ Black is fiddling with the move orders! Somehow I had to revisit many lines which I managed to avoid with the same move tricks 😀... }
6. Nc3
