{ An useful inclusion as taking on f3 would play into our hands. } 5... Bh5 6.
d3
{ The knight will be well placed on d2 and we can slowly fight for center control with c4. }
6... Nbd7 7. Nbd2 Bd6 8. g4 Bg6 9. g5 { Showing the power of the bishop. } 9...
Nh5 10. Rg1 { followed by Nh4 winning the bishop pair and a nice game. } *

