3... Bh5 4. h4
{ Nepo is fighting a lonely battle in this line...Let's also join in on the fun! }
4... Qd6 5. d4
{ In this line we just get used to the fact that our king is fighting piece! }
5... Qg3+ 6. Kd2 f6 7. e3
{ The joy of the queen on g3 was always going to be very short lived. } 7...
Nc6 8. Ne2 { "Go back queen!" } 8... Qd6 9. Kc1
{ A new form of "Artificial castling!" } 9... O-O-O 10. Ba3 Qd7 11. Nbc3
{ and the king will be very safe on b2. It is fine to be greedy here and play on all flanks :@@EndBracket@@. I give you permission to "Unleash the Beast!" }
