{ Nepo is fighting a lonely battle in this line...Let's also join in on the fun! }
4... f6 { This is the move I faced most in my bullet run. } 5. d4 e5 6. Nc3
{ Once again Nc3 let's go! } 6... Bd6 7. e4 { This is pure central fight! }
7... exd4 8. Qxd4 Bg3+ 9. Kd1 { The king will be quite safe on c1. } 9... Ne7
10. exd5
{ King is already in the centre... Let's at least grab a pawn in return! }
10... Be5 11. Qd2 Bxc3 12. Bxc3 Nxd5 13. Kc1
{ followed by Kb2 and a slight advantage. } *

