{ Fighting for the centre control leading to a transposition. } 7... e6 8. Nd2
Bd6
{ 8...Nxd4  9.Bxd4  dxc4  10.bxc4!  Changing the character of the game and with good play along the b-file. }
9. cxd5 Nxd4 10. Bxd4 exd5 11. Bd3
{ We get our Isolani structure and beautiful bishops controlling the whole board. }
