1. b3
{ We just give Black the centre, a false sense of security... Only to take all of them back with interest at the right time! }
1... d5 2. Bb2 c5
{ Black starts the fight for the centre. I came up with the name Ozmin Attack @@StartBracket@@which is just Nimzo put in reverse order@@EndBracket@@ thanks to the help of my discord members 😀. }
3. e3 { One way to continue the fight for the e5-square is with } 3... a6
{ Stopping any Bb5 nonsense and preparing to develop Nc6 next. } 4. Nf3 Nc6 5.
d4
{ Since Black has wasted a tempo on prophylaxis, we use the time to open up the centre! If  5.Be2  d4!  Taking over the centre! }
5... e6 6. c4 { Taking the fight to the centre! } 6... Nf6
{ If  6...cxd4  then  7.Nxd4  Bb4+  8.Nd2  with a good position as the pin along a5-e1 diagonal can't be used to gain anything. }
7. cxd5 exd5 8. Nbd2
