9... f5 10. Nd3 { with a slightly better position. } 10... Qe7 11. Nc3 b6
{ Activating the bishop as the other way with Bd7-e8-h5 is way too time consuming. }
12. Rc1 Bb7 13. e3
{ with good control over the centre and ideas like Rc2-Qc1 or Qa1. } *

