16... c4 17. Qc2
{ with a new position, I have never seen such a structure until to this day :@@EndBracket@@. The pawn on a4 helps in our fight on the queenside. }
17... Rc8 18. dxc4 { The right time. } 18... dxc4
{ Otherwise we get the Isolani structure. } 19. Rfd1 Qc7
{ Only move without which Black is toast! } 20. Ng5 g6 { Once again forced! }
21. Qc3 { with a complex fight! } *

